This code system http://nhn.no/fhir/nilar/CodeSystem/id-provider-cs defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition

name: IdProvider_CS
title: Id Provider CS
description: Various resources has one or two identifiers, provided by requester or service provider. These are the naming systems used to represent the origins of the identifiers.
